{"tid":2232302,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母 你當過我係姐妹？","createTime":"2020-10-06T09:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T03:18:26.000Z","uid":136738,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7f2fb8d18b9171dcc8e72994dbced789f7d738a2","tid":2232302,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:41:56.000Z","msg":"你出佐事叫我黎，<br />\n我即刻過黎搵你<br />\n咩事都無講就被人捉住打佐獲，<br />\n真係OP！<br />\n<br />\n人地一個拉住我，跟住後面幾個人過黎一齊打<br />\n你老味你居然企系度睇？<br />\n<br />\n我被人打你跑到仲快過隻狗，<br />\n真係好撚嘢！<br />\n你呢個朋友真係做得過！<br />\n我咁幫你！你咁樣對我？<br />\n宜家我一個人訓系草叢度 你知唔知道我幾驚？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母以後唔會再邀你打傳說對決"},{"pid":"dae7b17b6920ea103a82cd6ad926c7f55caa205c","tid":2232302,"uid":134171,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Cb8S3Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Cb8S3Z.jpg&h=b4999ae3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c731efe5e1240b34d41749150b94264ff0f47149","tid":2232302,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dae7b17b6920ea103a82cd6ad926c7f55caa205c","tid":2232302,"uid":134171,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Cb8S3Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Cb8S3Z.jpg&h=b4999ae3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45574c31bdbaa43a2ce01505dd4eab19c23d6d71","tid":2232302,"uid":90615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:47:42.000Z","msg":"新品種波品狗<br />\n娛台狗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df8cae3bf8322355e12b892fab42b074c9da626","tid":2232302,"uid":90615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:48:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新品種波台